description: Creates a template alias for a template.

parameters.name: AwsAccountId
parameters.description: The ID of the Amazon Web Services account that contains the template that you creating an alias for.

parameters.name: AliasName
parameters.description: The name that you want to give to the template alias that you're creating. Don't start the alias name with the $ character. Alias names that start with $ are reserved by Amazon QuickSight.

parameters.name: TemplateVersionNumber
parameters.description: The version number of the template.

nested_items.name: AliasName
nested_items.description: The display name of the template alias.

nested_items.name: Arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the template alias.

nested_items.name: TemplateVersionNumber
nested_items.description: The version number of the template alias.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: The HTTP status of the request.

nested_items.name: RequestId
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services request ID for this operation.
